<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 18:14:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登连任竞选不会停止使用 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bidens-re-election-campaign-wont-stop-using-tiktok-2024-04-24/</link><description>周三，一位竞选官员表示，乔·拜登的连任竞选活动计划继续使用 TikTok，此前不久，美国总统签署了一项法案，如果该应用程序的中国所有者未能剥离该应用程序，该法案将禁止该应用程序。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 17:23:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bidens-re-election-campaign-wont-stop-using-tiktok-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>受中国市场推动，意大利 Moncler 第一季度销售额增长 16%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-italys-moncler-up-16-first-quarter-boosted-by-china-2024-04-24/</link><description>意大利时尚集团 Moncler 周三公布，按固定汇率计算，第一季度销售额增长 16%，这得益于中国强劲的需求，中国已成为一些奢侈品牌的痛处。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-italys-moncler-up-16-first-quarter-boosted-by-china-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国缓慢复苏给奢侈品行业前景蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-sector-outlook-clouded-by-chinas-slow-recovery-2024-04-24/</link><description>欧洲大型奢侈品牌的最新销售数据并不能让人相信中国对高端时尚的需求正在复苏，这给该行业的前景蒙上了一层阴影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-sector-outlook-clouded-by-chinas-slow-recovery-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok首席执行官预计将击败美国禁令：“我们哪儿也不去”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-ceo-expects-defeat-us-restrictions-we-arent-going-anywhere-2024-04-24/</link><description>TikTok 首席执行官周三表示，该公司预计将赢得一项法律挑战，以阻止总统乔·拜登签署的立法，他表示该法案将禁止 1.7 亿美国人使用的流行短视频应用程序。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:23:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-ceo-expects-defeat-us-restrictions-we-arent-going-anywhere-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>由于欧盟的担忧，TikTok 暂停了新应用程序的奖励计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-suspend-tiktok-lites-reward-programme-amid-eu-concerns-2024-04-24/</link><description>周三，该公司在 X 社交媒体平台上表示，TikTok 将自愿暂停其新应用程序 TikTok Lite 的奖励计划，同时试图解决欧盟的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-suspend-tiktok-lites-reward-programme-amid-eu-concerns-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>德国间谍机构警告企业不要对中国过于“天真”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-spy-agency-warns-companies-against-being-too-naive-china-2024-04-24/</link><description>德国国内间谍机构周三告诉企业，他们应该警惕北京的工业间谍活动，警告他们不要天真或过度依赖中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-spy-agency-warns-companies-against-being-too-naive-china-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>智利取代阿根廷成为 2025 年田径世锦赛主办国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/chile-replace-argentina-2025-track-world-championships-hosts-2024-04-24/</link><description>国际自行车联盟（UCI）周三表示，2025 年场地自行车世界锦标赛将在智利圣地亚哥举行，而不是之前宣布的在阿根廷圣胡安举行。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:31:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/chile-replace-argentina-2025-track-world-championships-hosts-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>ASML首席执行官表示美国限制维修部分中国设备不会影响盈利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-us-restricts-servicing-some-china-equipment-wont-hurt-earnings-2024-04-24/</link><description>顶级半导体设备供应商ASML即将卸任的首席执行官周三表示，美国政府将阻止该公司在某些情况下对此前出售给中国客户的部分机器进行维修。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:08:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-us-restricts-servicing-some-china-equipment-wont-hurt-earnings-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行表示，中国财富的增长推动了客户在美国的投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-says-growing-chinese-wealth-fuels-client-investments-us-2024-04-24/</link><description>汇丰银行美国和美洲区首席执行官迈克尔·罗伯茨表示，汇丰银行在中国和香港的富裕客户仍然渴望在美国投资。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-says-growing-chinese-wealth-fuels-client-investments-us-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>科威尔期待水手队晋级亚洲冠军联赛决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popp-hero-10-man-marinos-advance-asian-champions-league-final-2024-04-24/</link><description>哈里·科威尔周三带领日本横滨水手队通过点球大战战胜韩国蔚山现代队，首次进入亚洲冠军联赛决赛，他的目标是创造横滨水手队的历史。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 13:29:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popp-hero-10-man-marinos-advance-asian-champions-league-final-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>在亚洲文化热潮中，年轻的俄罗斯人随着韩国流行音乐跳舞并观看动漫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/young-russians-dance-k-pop-watch-anime-amid-asian-culture-boom-2024-04-24/</link><description>几年前，当卡琳娜·马拉克希娜 (Karina Marakshina) 被要求描述她莫斯科舞蹈工作室的音乐风格时，她必须解释什么是韩国流行音乐。现在，她说她几乎在每一个购物的商场里都能听到这种声音。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 13:17:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/young-russians-dance-k-pop-watch-anime-amid-asian-culture-boom-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>肖尔茨在涉嫌中国间谍被捕后表示，德国不能接受间谍活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-cannot-accept-spying-says-scholz-after-suspected-china-spy-arrested-2024-04-24/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨在一名极右翼政客的助手因涉嫌为中国从事间谍活动而被捕后表示，德国不能接受外国的间谍活动，并将努力确保责任人受到审判。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 12:31:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-cannot-accept-spying-says-scholz-after-suspected-china-spy-arrested-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国间谍指控欧盟民意调查前加强对德国极右翼分子的审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-spy-charges-up-scrutiny-germanys-far-right-ahead-eu-polls-2024-04-24/</link><description>泄露了有关大规模驱逐计划的讨论。使用纳粹语言的审判。现在，中国正在监视有关克里姆林宫盟友秘密付款的指控和报告。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 12:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-spy-charges-up-scrutiny-germanys-far-right-ahead-eu-polls-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>托斯卡纳的奢侈品供应商感受到来自中国和不断变化的趋势的寒意</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tuscanys-luxury-suppliers-feel-chill-china-changing-trends-2024-04-24/</link><description>中国对奢侈品的需求下降加剧了托斯卡纳传统皮革公司的问题，因为它们供应的大型时装公司正在重塑战略，导致痛苦的裁员，而这可能只是一个开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 11:03:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tuscanys-luxury-suppliers-feel-chill-china-changing-trends-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃如何在贸易战中将廉价的中国电动汽车登陆美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-volvo-landed-cheap-chinese-ev-us-shores-trade-war-2024-04-24/</link><description>一款中国制造的电动汽车将于今年夏天登陆美国经销商，其动力和效率与全球最畅销的电动汽车特斯拉 Model Y 类似，但价格便宜约 8,000 美元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 10:05:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-volvo-landed-cheap-chinese-ev-us-shores-trade-war-2024-04-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>